data.description: Fantastic Opportunity!! This 4bed and 2 bath Split Level home located in Heatherwood Subdivision is now looking for its new owner!! Step into this delightful traditional home boasting four bedrooms and two bathrooms. The charming exterior beckons with its classic appeal, while inside, you'll find a seamless blend of comfort and functionality. Enjoy gatherings in the living room and savor homemade meals in the inviting kitchen. Retreat to cozy bedrooms, including a serene primary suite with its private bathroom. Outside, discover a tranquil backyard oasis perfect for relaxation or entertaining. This home offers timeless warmth and comfort for you and your loved ones. Hurry and Bring your offers!!! This home won't last long.
